[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Enroll a patient into the support program. Validates
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     eligibility, captures mental-health-specific consent,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     initializes the longitudinal store, and emits the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     enrollment event.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Step 1A: validate eligibility against institutional
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # exclusion criteria. Patients outside the bot's scope
