[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Compose the response. Production wires this through
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     bedrock_agent_runtime.invoke_agent with the support
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     tools defined as action groups; the demo uses the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     mock that demonstrates the structure.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
