[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2675[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2676[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     During crisis pathway, only permitted response types
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2677[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     are allowed. Therapy-attempted, trauma-processing, and
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2678[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     extended-emotional-processing are forbidden.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2679[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2680[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     text_lower = response_text.lower()
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2681[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
