[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2731[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2732[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Step 6: Persist the Support-Decision Records, Sensitive-Disclosure Records, and Longitudinal Updates
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2733[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2734[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The conversation log captures the dialog. The support-decision-record journal captures, separately, every support decision (therapeutic-content delivery, safety-plan reference, symptom-log update, crisis-pathway engagement, warm-handoff initiation, mandatory-report routing) with version stamps. The sensitive-disclosure store, separately keyed and access-restricted, captures sensitive disclosures with appropriate handling. The longitudinal store is updated with stated preference changes, symptom tracking, and the conversation summary.
