[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3102[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     mental-health outcome attribution is harder than
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3103[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     chronic-disease attribution and the analysis is
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3104[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     suggestive rather than causal. The demo records the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3105[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     queue entry.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3106[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3107[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # Outcome correlation for mental-health support is
